'''Belgium''' (fr. - Belgique) yɛ ɔman u [[Yurop]]. N'ahenkuro ye [[Brussels]].

Belgium yɛ ɔman kuruwaa a ɛwɔ Yurop asaasepɔn atɔe so. Ɔman yi asaase kɛsi yɛ 30,528 sokwɛɛ(528 sq mi). Ɔman yi mu nipa dodoɔ nyinaa yɛ ɔpepem dubaako(11 million). Kasapɔn baanu na wɔka wɔ ɔman yi mu : Dutch kasaa ni French kasaa. Ɔman no epueɛ no, wɔ ka German fo kasaa. Belgium wɔ mantaw edu. 

* Asaase tɛtrɛɛtɛ: 30 528 km²
* Omanmu nipa dodoɔ: 11 303 528  (2017)

